        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13788950/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13788950/" class="">第7页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/17531670/" class=" " title="jakolo">jakolo</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13788950">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">政治的素材是人。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13788950/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-07-19 21:35</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>政治的素材是人。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







